You're obviously in lots
of video, your own and

00:27:45.080 --> 00:27:45.820
"Numberphile".

00:27:45.820 --> 00:27:47.370
Do you read comments?

00:27:47.370 --> 00:27:50.990
JAMES GRIME: I read all the
comments on my own channel,

00:27:50.990 --> 00:27:53.520
the comments and the
messages I get.

00:27:53.520 --> 00:27:55.895
And I'm not always able
to answer them all.

00:27:55.895 --> 00:27:58.520
Even if I did, I mean, I
just don't have time

00:27:58.520 --> 00:27:59.100
to answer them all.

